									<h5 id="subject_150516">
										<a href="http://fantasy-faction.com/forum/(aug-2016)-potions-and-elixirs/(aug-2016)-potions-and-elixirs-submission-thread/msg150516/#msg150516" rel="nofollow">Re: [Aug 2016] - Potions and Elixirs - Submission Thread</a>
									</h5>
									<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>Reply #8 on:</strong> August 19, 2016, 07:29:40 PM &#187;</div>
									<div id="msg_150516_quick_mod"></div>
								</div>
