									<h5 id="subject_150528">
										<a href="http://fantasy-faction.com/forum/(aug-2016)-potions-and-elixirs/(aug-2016)-potions-and-elixirs-submission-thread/msg150528/#msg150528" rel="nofollow">Re: [Aug 2016] - Potions and Elixirs - Submission Thread</a>
									</h5>
									<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>Reply #9 on:</strong> August 19, 2016, 09:38:17 PM &#187;</div>
									<div id="msg_150528_quick_mod"></div>
